      <description>I hope it's not just killing the "final boss" of an expansion but more like a collection quest from raid bosses and at the end of that collection quest another final epic encounter spawns that unlocks the new expansion.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Example:&lt;br&gt;A rare item collector desires certain artifacts from certain creatures in the world.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A Globule of Sheer Terror from Cazic-Thule&lt;br&gt;A Black Banshee's Heart from Innoruuk&lt;br&gt;A Searing Dragon's Fang from Lord Nagafen&lt;br&gt;A Frozen Dragon Heartstring from Lady Vox&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Bring them all back to the collector and he rewards you with an accursed map that he acquired off of a sailor that had gone mad after a voyage he made.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;After receiving the map and "opening" it, the Ghost of a Great Shissar Warlord spawns and attacks you (and should you fail the encounter anyone who was in the party after spawning it will be able to hail the collector again after he respawns and spawn it again).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;After defeating the Shissar you loot the map and upon identifying it, it suggests that you deliver this map to a ship's captain, then a worldwide emote sounds, "Upon the discovery of a strange map, the city of Qeynos is announcing a discovery mission to an unknown continent" and one week later, BOOM, Kunark.&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
